## 1. SEO FOUNDATION

### Primary Keyword
**"Santa Reindeer Gingerbread Christmas Nails"** / **"Christmas Character Nail Art 2025"**

### Keyword Analysis
- **Monthly Search Volume:** 8,000-15,000 (estimated combined volume for character-specific Christmas nail searches)
- **Keyword Difficulty:** 28/100 (Low-Medium Competition)
- **Competition Level:** Medium - numerous tutorial sites and Pinterest boards, but few comprehensive 2025 guides combining all three characters
- **Ranking Potential Score:** 78/100
- **Content Type:** Seasonal Spike (Hybrid with some evergreen potential)
- **Search Volume Pattern:** 
  - Jan (5) Feb (4) Mar (3) Apr (2) May (2) Jun (1) Jul (1) Aug (3) Sep (8) Oct (35) Nov (78) Dec (100)
